data.actual_result: The action type and keybind gets messed up, and make its impossible to remove
data.expected_result: It should carry over keybind settings
data.short_description: On the new Electron update, keybinds gets messed up with different actions/keybinds than set
data.steps_to_repro: - Have a keybind before the update (I had Press to mute set on mouse 4) - Observe how it changed to something random, and is not delete-able (It changed to "PRESS TO TALK" and to control 4, and pressing both buttons did nothing besides making the sound when unmuting)
